# 📸 Screenshots Folder

This folder contains project screenshots for the README.

## 📋 Required Screenshots

Please add the following screenshots to this folder:

### Main Scoreboard
- `scoreboard-main.png` - Main scoreboard interface
- `scoreboard-match.png` - Match in progress
- `scoreboard-victory.png` - Victory animation

### Smart Grouping
- `grouping-input.png` - Player input interface
- `grouping-result.png` - Grouping results
- `grouping-start.png` - Start match from grouping

### Statistics
- `history-records.png` - Match history
- `leaderboard.png` - Player leaderboard
- `skill-analysis.png` - Skill analysis charts

### Themes
- `theme-purple.png` - Night Purple theme
- `theme-orange.png` - Vibrant Orange theme
- `theme-blue.png` - Sky Blue theme
- `theme-green.png` - Forest Green theme
- `theme-pink.png` - Sakura Pink theme
- `theme-blackgold.png` - Black Gold theme

## 📏 Screenshot Guidelines

- **Size**: 390-428px width (mobile optimized)
- **Format**: PNG preferred
- **Size**: < 500KB each (compress if needed)
- **Content**: Use sample data, no personal info

## 🔗 How to Take Screenshots

Visit: https://1822520752.github.io/badmintonrapidscoreboard/

Use browser DevTools (F12) → Device Mode (Ctrl+Shift+M) → Take screenshot

See `screenshots/README.md` for detailed instructions.
